cross: Paphiopedilum Chou-Yi Charles x Paphiopedilum Impulse
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: One exceptional, large flat flower on one 20-cm black, hirsute inflorescence; sepals intensely saturated deep burgundy, dorsal sepal extremely flat; petals deep burgundy, black hirsute edges; lip intense burgundy; staminode pink; substance very firm; texture glossy.
